==設施==
清水灣鄉村俱樂部設有不同種類的體育及康樂設施，如：高爾夫球場及練習場、推桿果嶺、健身室、水療設施、室外泳池、網球場、乒乓球室、羽毛球場、壁球場、籃球場及足球場等。

另外，會所亦有多所餐飲設施，包括Oasis<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-oasis.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - Oasis |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107035257/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-oasis.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、觀瀾樓<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-ocean-view.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - Ocean View |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106053846/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-ocean-view.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、Horizons<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-Horizons.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - Horizons |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107101141/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-Horizons.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、Poolside Cafe<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-Poolside-Cafe.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - Poolside Cafe |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107091205/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-Poolside-Cafe.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、BreeZes<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-BreeZes.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - BreeZes |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107024743/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-BreeZes.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，以及Wine Cellar<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-wine-cellar.aspx |title=The Clearwater Bay Golf and Country Club - Wine Cellar |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106213014/http://www.cwbgolf.org/fnb-wine-cellar.aspx |archive-date=2016-01-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

其他設施包括Pro Shop、Country Club、 多功能活動室、Oasis草坪、兒童遊樂室及室外遊樂場等。

